narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Learned a lot about making and evaluating art. really enjoyed taking the class and learning how to do shop and think about art making!

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Professor Tubergen is an incredibly patient teacher in shop and really cares about everyone accessing the material and the shop. Enjoyed how art making was paired with discussion sections. Perhaps might have enjoyed more assignments with more focus, but also was great diving in depth to three assignments.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Fantastic course, Elizabeth is a great teacher. Take it if you get the chance!
Very much! Really awesome to practice a different kind of thinking.
